name: Erect Horse Penis - Concept LoRA
description:
Please, check the description, there is plenty of useful information.

Flaccid Horse Penis LoRA - Flaccid version of horse penis LoRA

As you can see, now it's separated concepts, flaccid, erect, etc.

What different from another horse penis LoRAs?

It's different from those i've tested.

  1. Don't touching original model style.

  2. Compatibility. Works pretty well with different LoRAs, like characters or even style.

  3. Works great for both male and female characters.

  4. Diversity in sizes, ability to control size / color.

Indroduction:

Erect horse penis LoRA. Works pretty good with other LoRAs and humanoid characters.

Model used for previews: DivineAnimeMix1

Recommendations:

  • 1.0 weight for most models

  • See relevant tag tips

Relevant genital tag tips:

Google Docs page, contains older prompt tips (v1 - v3).

Erect Horse Penis (v4)

You can adjust tag weight by placing it in brackets and specify value: (Erection:1.4), where 1.4 is a modifier. Base tag weight is 1.0 on being put to your prompt box..

So, Large Penis and (Large Penis:1.4) would produce different sized schlongs. The second one also can be much bigger or equal to Huge Penis.

You can combine tags below as you like to get the result you need.

Smallest possible penis - Big, the stallionis maximus - Gigantic

  • Eqcok as "support" activation tags, may lead to bigger penises

  • Erection | Size Penis for penis state and size

    • Size value can be Big | Large | Huge or Gigantic

    • You can use both size tags at once to achieve “middle” result

  • Size Testicles for testicles size

    • Size value can be Big | Large | Huge or Gigantic

    • You can use two tags at once to achieve “middle” result

  • Sagging | Resting Testicles for testicles state

    • Sagging for saggy testicles

    • Resting for on-surface state (like breast rest)

  • Autopaizuri for penis between breasts

    • Don't use this tag alongside with Erection or Size Penis

  • Autofellatio + Oral | Blowjob | Licking Penis for self fellatio

    • You may use all three fellatio tags for higher change of autofellatio

    • Don't use this tag alongside with Erection or Size Penis

  • Cock Sheath for proper penis sheath

  • Blunt Tip | Flared Tip for penis tip shape

    • Blunt Tip for more flat tip

    • Flared Tip for more bulgy tip

    • Add undesired one in negatives, it should help, like (flared tip:1.2)

  • Thick Penis | Thin Penis for penis girth

    • May be unstable, need further improvements

  • Long Penis | Short Penis for penis lenght

    • May be unstable, need further improvements

  • Urethra for better urethra placement

Colors:

  • Skin-colored Penis | Testicles for regular skin-toned endowment

  • Dark Penis | Testicles for more dark penis or testicles

  • Color Penis | Testicles for your color

Some colors may perform better than others. If you're getting the same color every time, just add it to negative prompt. Never forget about negatives. It would do the trick.

Example penis prompts (v4):

For big erect penis:

  • (big penis, big testicles:1.2), (blunt tip, urethra:1.2), cock sheath

For large erect penis:

  • large penis, large testicles, (blunt tip, urethra:1.2), cock sheath

For huge erect penis:

  • eqcok, erection, (huge penis, huge testicles:1.2), (blunt tip, urethra:1.2), cock sheat

For autopaizuri + autofellatio:

  • large testicles, autopaizuri, autofellatio, blowjob, oral, licking penis

If you want make less messy/dripping/wet penises, just type:

  • (precum, cum, wet, suggestive fluid:1.2) in your negative prompt

Credits:

Trained on NAI Anime Full.

Dataset of 150 pictures (v1), 8 epochs, Clip Skip - 1
Dataset of 224 pictures (v2), 14 epochs, Clip Skip - 2
Dataset of 160 pictures (v3), 10 epochs, Clip Skip - 2
Dataset of 300 pictures (v4), 10 epochs, Clip Skip - 2

Really big thanks to:

  • Some good folks from Discord server

  • You, for reading, downloading and reviewing this LoRA

modelVersions.name: Erect Horse Penis v3
modelVersions.description:
Dataset now would be separated on two versions, flaccid penis and erect penis. Soon i'll try to do more with Horse Penis states. As i found out, it's almost impossible to do the same level controls over conflicting concepts like flaccid / erect / fully sheathed penises with lack of dataset, so i decided to separate it.

Erect version is for: Erect Penis, Autopaizuri and Autofellatio concepts.

Talking about advantages:

  • More accurate horse penises

  • More accurate and versatile dataset

  • More accurate urethra position, appears more often

  • Easier control over penis size, more options

  • Easier control over dataset and further imrpovements for me

  • Better Style LoRA compatibility

  • Less glitches on testicles

  • Less "Latex" effect of sheath and testicles

  • Less random and distorted hands on shafts

Talking about disadvantages:

  • Affects style a little bit more than v1 or v2, would be improved in future

  • All-in-one LoRA no more

  • Less veins on penises
